_sText:
This is a pretty simple gungame map made with a space theme. It's basically a giant ring with a center sphere area. Also, all glass in this map does not block bullets. PS: watch for the flying xwing outside put in there for the lolz.

Thanks to Quinity for his space skybox and [-B-] for his halo textures.

If you upload this map to your server or use it as inspiration for your own map, please post here or pm me.
